{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"161ae5d6e4","title":"大字报——我们要争平等地位","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"85f3614e6e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"161ae5d6e4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f61eadb28f","name":"太原工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7e92cc8cea","type":"title","text":"大字报——我们要争平等地位","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"161ae5d6e4"},{"id":"5a5f9db971","type":"authors","text":"太原工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"161ae5d6e4"},{"id":"c43784cbb4","type":"paragraph","text":"学校内领导上把同学分成三等人，党、团、落后群众。党员总是高人一等。团员也有先进落后之分，学校的党、团和行政做工作，只依靠少数的党、团干部，本不接近少数群众，只是少数人的汇报，有什么大小工作，党、团干部包办，根本不用民主选举而委任党、团干部领导。好像群众中根本是白痴，没有领导天才，我们请问这是平等看待吗？是相信群众吗？他们口口声声是马列主义，实际上官僚主义、宗派主义。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"161ae5d6e4"},{"id":"e4117791bc","type":"paragraph","text":" 太原工学院  ×××","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"161ae5d6e4"}],"page":{"id":"4fc034bcca","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"161ae5d6e4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}